  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Ragdoll Playground!</h2>What could be better than levels in the playground format filled with dynamic obstacles and destructible walls? Probably only two levels with obstacles and destructible walls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218700/extras/19784cf3afee4e1cae8a1d7b0c4878ec.poster.avif?t=1729436390\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218700/extras/19784cf3afee4e1cae8a1d7b0c4878ec.webm?t=1729436390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218700/extras/19784cf3afee4e1cae8a1d7b0c4878ec.mp4?t=1729436390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What can I do in the game?</h2>Everything is possible in this game! Well, or almost everything. Fall in slow motion, destroy huge towers, pass obstacle courses, fly into rides and all this with realistic physics.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lots of characters<br></li><li>Different levels and open locations<br></li><li>Dynamic rides<br></li><li>Physical interaction with objects<br></li><li>Time dilation<br></li><li>Unpredictable situations<br></li><li>Character Physics Settings<br></li><li>Unlimited gameplay</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Ragdoll Playground!</h2>What could be better than levels in the playground format filled with dynamic obstacles and destructible walls? Probably only two levels with obstacles and destructible walls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218700/extras/19784cf3afee4e1cae8a1d7b0c4878ec.poster.avif?t=1729436390\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218700/extras/19784cf3afee4e1cae8a1d7b0c4878ec.webm?t=1729436390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218700/extras/19784cf3afee4e1cae8a1d7b0c4878ec.mp4?t=1729436390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What can I do in the game?</h2>Everything is possible in this game! Well, or almost everything. Fall in slow motion, destroy huge towers, pass obstacle courses, fly into rides and all this with realistic physics.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lots of characters<br></li><li>Different levels and open locations<br></li><li>Dynamic rides<br></li><li>Physical interaction with objects<br></li><li>Time dilation<br></li><li>Unpredictable situations<br></li><li>Character Physics Settings<br></li><li>Unlimited gameplay</li></ul>",
